  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the ability of semi‐automated plaque assessment in cardiac computed tomography
      angiography (CCTA) and high sensitive troponin T (hsTnT) for the risk stratification of
      patients at intermediate risk for coronary artery disease (CAD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
